Ingredients
1   recipe Scratch Pie Crust, for double pie crust
½ cup (125 mL) sugar
2 tbsp (30 mL) all-purpose flour
1 tsp (5 mL) Korintje Cinnamon or ground cinnamon
4   medium baking apples, peeled, cored, and sliced (about 4 cups/1 L) (Braeburn or Granny Smith apples work well, or you can use a combination)
½   lemon
1 tbsp (15 mL) butter or margarine
1 tbsp (15 mL) milk
Optional: 2 tsp (10 mL) sugar
